OL,3,CEx-Fujitsu boss 'aggrieved' after
OL,4,Cthinking Horizon was major success
OL,6,FA former boss of Fujitsu has told the
OL,7,FPost Office Inquiry he feels
OL,8,F"aggrieved" after initially believing
OL,9,Fthe Horizon system was one of the
OL,10,Fcompany's "major successes".
OL,12,FRichard Christou said he took no
OL,13,Fresponsibility for the scandal, which
OL,14,Fhas since been described as one of the
OL,15,Fbiggest miscarriages of justice in
OL,16,FBritish legal history.
OL,18,FMr Christou, who was chief executive
OL,19,Fof the company between 2000 and 2004,
OL,20,Fsaid he always regarded the Post
OL,21,FOffice as a "satisfied customer".
