OL,3,CEx-Fujitsu boss 'aggrieved' after
OL,4,Cthinking Horizon was major success
OL,6,FHe told the probe he "knew nothing
OL,7,Fabout it" while he was the head of
OL,8,FInternational Computers Ltd (ICL),
OL,9,Fwhich later became Fujitsu, when
OL,10,Faddressing his accountability for the
OL,11,Fmiscarriages of justice.
OL,13,FCounsel to the inquiry Sam Stevens
OL,14,Fthen asked Mr Christou how he would
OL,15,Fdescribe his "level of accountability"
OL,16,Fin terms of the ICL Group and its
OL,17,Foperations.
