OL,3,CEx-Fujitsu boss 'aggrieved' after
OL,4,Cthinking Horizon was major success
OL,6,FMr Christou replied: "What I was
OL,7,Fresponsible for was that, so far as
OL,8,Fpossible, to see that the operations
OL,9,Fof ICL were carried out legally, were
OL,10,Fcarried out profitably, and to report
OL,11,Fto my shareholders, Fujitsu Ltd,
OL,12,Fvarious issues in so far as it was
OL,13,Fnecessary.
OL,15,F"If you mean that I was responsible
OL,16,Ffor the miscarriage of justice, then I
OL,17,Fdon't accept that.
OL,19,F"It's not to mitigate the miscarriage
OL,20,Fof justice, I hasten to add, I think
OL,21,Fit's a gross miscarriage of justice.
