OL,3,CEx-Fujitsu boss 'aggrieved' after
OL,4,Cthinking Horizon was major success
OL,6,F"I really feel for the sub-postmasters
OL,7,Fand the postmasters involved ` but
OL,8,Ftalking about accountability is a
OL,9,Fdifferent matter.
OL,11,F"And certainly I knew nothing about
OL,12,Fit."
OL,14,FIn his witness statement to the
OL,15,Finquiry, Mr Christou added: "No
OL,16,Ffurther problems were raised with me
OL,17,Fin connection with Horizon during my
OL,18,Ftime with Fujitsu.
