OL,3,CEx-Fujitsu boss 'aggrieved' after
OL,4,Cthinking Horizon was major success
OL,6,F"In particular, I had no knowledge of
OL,7,Fthe prosecution of postmasters by (the
OL,8,FPost Office).
OL,10,F"I always regarded Horizon as one of
OL,11,F(Fujitsu's) major successes, with (the
OL,12,FPost Office) as a satisfied customer."
OL,14,FUnder questioning from Flora Page, a
OL,15,Flawyer representing a number of
OL,16,Fsubpostmasters, Mr Christou was
OL,17,Fpressed again on his accountability.
OL,19,FMs Page asked: "You don't take any
OL,20,Fresponsibility?"
