OL,3,CEx-Fujitsu boss 'aggrieved' after
OL,4,Cthinking Horizon was major success
OL,6,FMr Christou replied: "No. I'm not
OL,7,Fmitigating that there is a gross
OL,8,Fmiscarriage of justice ` and if you
OL,9,Fthink I don't feel for the postmasters
OL,10,Fand the sub-postmasters, you're wrong.
OL,12,F"I do feel ` and I also feel aggrieved
OL,13,Fthat what I felt was a good system has
OL,14,Fbeen put into such disrepute.
OL,16,F"But I'm not responsible for it, and
OL,17,FI've said before that the real issue
OL,18,Fis the way the prosecutions were
OL,19,Fhandled and the flows of information."
