OL,3,CEx-Fujitsu boss 'aggrieved' after
OL,4,Cthinking Horizon was major success
OL,6,FMore than 700 sub-postmasters were
OL,7,Fprosecuted by the Post Office and
OL,8,Fhanded criminal convictions between
OL,9,F1999 and 2015 as Fujitsu's faulty
OL,10,Fsystem made it appear as though money
OL,11,Fwas missing at their branches.
OL,13,FHundreds of victims are awaiting
OL,14,Fcompensation despite the Government
OL,15,Fannouncing that those who have had
OL,16,Fconvictions quashed are eligible for
OL,17,F#600,000 payouts.
